cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.DL 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with natural language processing and specifically focuses on assessing sentence-level prompt relevance in learner essays. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper evaluates various systems using neural embeddings and neural compositional models. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is relevant as the paper deals with estimating topical relevance in learner essays. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper proposes a new method for sentence-level similarity calculation using pre-trained word embeddings. 
- cs.DL (Deep Learning) is relevant as the paper uses neural embeddings and neural compositional models for the task.
